[
    {
        "content": "<p>myunbin opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12742\">PR #12742</a> from <code>myunbin:select-add-030926</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>This PR adds a batch of select simplification rules.</p>\n<p>Added rewrites:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code>(x == y) ? x : y =&gt; y</code></li>\n<li><code>(x | (y != z)) ? y : z =&gt; y</code></li>\n<li><code>(x == y) ? x : (x | y) =&gt; (x | y)</code></li>\n<li><code>(x != y) ? (x &amp; y) : y =&gt; (x &amp; y)</code></li>\n<li><code>(x &lt;_u y) ? 1 : (x == y) =&gt; (x &lt;=_u y)</code></li>\n<li><code>(x &lt; y) ? 1 : (x &gt; y) =&gt; (x != y)</code></li>\n<li><code>(x ? 1 : (x | y)) =&gt; (x ? 1 : y)</code></li>\n<li><code>if x == 1 then (y - 1) else (y - x) =&gt; (y - x)</code></li>\n<li><code>select(cond, eq(z, y), eq(p, y)) =&gt; eq(y, select(cond, z, p))</code></li>\n</ol>\n<p>These rewrites come from a synthesis project with @bongjunj (details: #10979 ).</p>\n<p>I grouped these into one PR to reduce overhead from many small PRs. <br>\nIf you'd prefer splitting by rule family, I'm happy to do that.</p>\n<p>cc @bongjunj</p>\n</blockquote>",
